    "When Clawix runs with full access, it can edit any file on your computer and run commands over the network without your authorization. This significantly increases the risk of data loss, leaks, or unexpected behavior. Learn more about the elevated risks.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "When Clawix runs with full access, it can edit any file on your computer and run commands over the network without your authorization. This significantly increases the risk of data loss, leaks, or unexpected behavior. Learn more about the elevated risks."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Cuando Clawix se ejecuta con acceso total, puede editar cualquier archivo de tu ordenador y ejecutar comandos por la red sin tu autorización. Esto aumenta significativamente el riesgo de pérdida de datos, filtraciones o comportamientos inesperados. Más información sobre los riesgos elevados."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "When Clawix runs with full access, it can edit any file on your computer and run commands over the network without your authorization. This significantly increases the risk of data loss, leaks, or unexpected behavior. Learn more about the elevated risks."
